00:21:15,083 --> 00:21:16,750
Please, you can't
go through with this!

490
00:21:16,833 --> 00:21:19,291
[VIRGO] Sorry, but it's
mine. And as thanks,

491
00:21:19,375 --> 00:21:21,958
I'll fill Magnolia full
of holes, just for you.

492
00:21:22,041 --> 00:21:24,791
Listen. Before you guys go
through with the ceremony--

493
00:21:24,875 --> 00:21:28,875
[VIRGO] Right, before that I'll
fill the Library full of holes!

494
00:21:28,958 --> 00:21:31,625
[HAPPY] I don't think
she's gonna listen.

495
00:21:31,708 --> 00:21:36,583
[NATSU screaming]

496
00:21:37,583 --> 00:21:38,708
[BOTH]
Natsu!

497
00:21:38,791 --> 00:21:41,166
[NATSU groans]

498
00:21:41,250 --> 00:21:45,416
That was the longest fall ever.
What are you guys doin' here?

499
00:21:45,500 --> 00:21:47,083
And where is "here"?

500
00:21:47,166 --> 00:21:48,875
[HAPPY] We're in the
normal world, Natsu!

501
00:21:48,958 --> 00:21:50,416
In a library!

502
00:21:50,500 --> 00:21:52,916
But I bet you've never even
heard of one of those, have ya?

503
00:21:54,583 --> 00:21:55,583
[YUKINO]
She's gone!

504
00:21:55,666 --> 00:21:57,041
[HAPPY]
And she took the globe!

505
00:21:57,125 --> 00:21:58,708
It's gone for real.

506
00:21:58,791 --> 00:22:00,375
How in the heck are
we gonna get it back?

507
00:22:00,458 --> 00:22:01,541
[NATSU]
Get what back?

508
00:22:01,625 --> 00:22:04,125
[LEVY] So. What I was
gonna tell her...

509
00:22:04,208 --> 00:22:06,291
There's a catch
with the ceremony.

510
00:22:06,375 --> 00:22:08,500
I was trying to tell
her what it was.

511
00:22:08,583 --> 00:22:12,000
[LEVY] I saw a note in the
catalog that listed the globe.

512
00:22:12,083 --> 00:22:14,958
Celestial spirits can use
the Liberam to gain freedom,

513
00:22:15,041 --> 00:22:17,666
but it comes at a heavy price.

514
00:22:17,750 --> 00:22:22,041
Their lives will only last
12 days once it is done.

515
00:22:22,125 --> 00:22:24,125
[ALL gasp]

516
00:22:24,208 --> 00:22:25,750
Are you serious?

517
00:22:25,833 --> 00:22:28,500
[YUKINO]
It's going to kill them?

518
00:22:28,583 --> 00:22:32,083
[HAPPY] It's not really freedom
if you're not alive to enjoy it.

519
00:24:12,375 --> 00:24:14,750
[HAPPY] Oh man, this
fish smell is amazing!

520
00:24:14,833 --> 00:24:16,375
It's making me so hungry!

521
00:24:16,458 --> 00:24:19,000
[NATSU] But it's the magic
ghost fish, not the kind ya eat!

522
00:24:19,083 --> 00:24:20,250
[HAPPY]
So what?

523
00:24:20,333 --> 00:24:22,083
[NATSU] So, is it
really a fish if it talks

524
00:24:22,166 --> 00:24:23,208
and does other stuff?

525
00:24:23,291 --> 00:24:24,666
[HAPPY]
Sure why not?

526
00:24:24,750 --> 00:24:27,208
Show me one rule that says
fish aren't allowed to talk!

527
00:24:27,291 --> 00:24:28,500
[NATSU]
I see your point, but--

528
00:24:28,583 --> 00:24:30,166
[HAPPY] If they can talk,
it's even better!

529
00:24:30,250 --> 00:24:32,125
They can tell me how
delicious they are!

530
00:24:32,208 --> 00:24:33,625
[NATSU]
Now that's advertising!

531
00:24:33,708 --> 00:24:35,875
[NATSU, HAPPY]
Next Time: Hisui Rises!

532
00:24:35,958 --> 00:24:37,666
[HAPPY] Maybe they'll have
some great slogans like,

533
00:24:37,750 --> 00:24:39,791
"Eat me!" or "Fish is love!"

534
00:24:39,875 --> 00:24:41,750
[NATSU] Yeah, those
are totally awesome.

